Welcome to Dramabite. The DramaBite App and the DramaBite websites and
        applications (collectively referred to as the "Services")
        which linked to this Policy are operated by DramaBite Team (hereinafter
        referred to as "we" or "us"). This Policy describes
        how we process and protect your personal information. This Policy
may
be translated into other languages for your convenience, any
        translated version of this Policy conflicts against the English version,
        this English version prevails.
Our Services are only available to adult users. If you are a minor
        under the age of 18 (or the age of majority as defined by local law),
        please do not use our Services.
We reserves the right to change this Policy at any time without notice,
        so be sure to check this Policy regularly to understand how we use your
        information. By installing, using, registering to or otherwise accessing
        the services, you agree to the
updated Policy and give an explicit and informed consent to the
        processing of your personal data in accordance with the
updated Policy.
We suggest you read it in conjunction with our Terms of Services (the
        “Terms”). When you access or use
our
Services, you agree to our Policy and you consent to our
        collection, storage, use and disclosure of your personal information as
        we’ve set out in this Policy.
