6. Children Information
Our Services are only available to adult users. If you are a minor
        under the age of 18 (or the age of majority as defined by local law),
        please do not use our Services.
If you are the guardian of a minor and find that your child is using
        our Services, please contact us in time and we will assist in deleting
        all personal information of your child.
